Package: fsca
Title: French syntactic complexity analyser 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: Sys.Date()
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nathan",
           family = "Vandeweerd",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nathan.vandeweerd@uclouvain.be",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6498-9474"))
Description: This package extracts a list of syntactic units from a dependency
  parsed French sentence in CONLL format and calculates a variety of syntactic complexity
  measures.
